title: $:/plugins/linonetwo/visualization-dashboard/language/en-GB/

Name: Visualization Dashboard
Description: Dashboard showing gauge and diagram for events on calendar and wiki. Provides procedures and chart builder based on echarts, and a layout displaying the dashboard for statistic charts.
PluginConfigs: Plugin Configs
ConfigDescription: These settings let you customise the behaviour of "Visualization Dashboard" plugin.
VisualizationDashboardLayout/Caption: Visualization Dashboard
VisualizationDashboardLayout/Description: Dashboard containing statistic charts for your calendar events and wiki activity.
VisualizationDashboardLayout/Exit: Exit and back to default layout
VisualizationDashboardLayout/ExistingGaugesCount: Count of gauges
PrevWeek: Previous Week
Now: Now
NextWeek: Next week
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Button/Open/Caption: Create Gauge
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Button/Cancel/Caption: Cancel
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Button/Create/Caption: Create
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Caption: Quick create new gauge from templates
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Title/Caption: Title of the gauge
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Title/Description: Enter the title for the new gauge, each gauge is a note tiddler, thus need a unique title.
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Tags/Caption: Tags
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Tags/Description: Specify tags for the gauge tiddler, optional.
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Icon/Caption: Icon
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Icon/Description: Choose an icon for the gauge, optional, can be Emoji or SVG, or reference the SVG image tiddler using the transclude syntax.
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Caption/Caption: Caption
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Caption/Description: Provide a caption for the gauge, optional, fallback to title if not specified.
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Description/Caption: Description
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Description/Description: Describe the gauge in detail.
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Enabled/Caption: Enabled
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/Enabled/Description: Toggle to enable or disable the gauge.
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/targetTiddler/Caption: Target tiddler.
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/targetTiddler/Description: Tiddlers used by the visualization. For recurring trackers, the list is pre-filtered to recurring calendar entries.
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/targetTiddler/AvailableCaption: Available tiddlers
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/targetTiddler/Placeholder: Select a tiddler
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/targetTiddler/AddButton: Add
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/targetTiddler/SelectedCaption: Selected tiddlers
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/targetTiddlerFilter/Caption: Filter expression
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/targetTiddlerFilter/Description: TiddlyWiki filter expression to narrow down candidate tiddlers. Leave empty to show all tiddlers.
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/targetValue/Caption: Target value.
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/targetValue/Description: value used by the visualization logic, typically as denominator of a percentage, e.g. total hours, subject to the specific logic of the vis template
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/color/Caption: Color
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/color/Description: theme color of visualization, need to be a color code, you can pick it from the palette or enter it manually, like `#66ccff`
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/grid-column-span/Caption: Width
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/grid-column-span/Description: How many columns of width are occupied on the dashboard
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/grid-row-span/Caption: Height
Modal/CreateGaugeModal/grid-row-span/Description: How many rows of height are occupied on the dashboard
SystemTags: System Tags
Tag/Gauge/Caption: Gauge tag
Tag/Gauge/Description: Tiddlers with this tag will be recognized by this plugin and put into the dashboard.
Tag/GaugeTemplate/Caption: Gauge template tag
Tag/GaugeTemplate/Description: The tiddler will be listed in the list of templates in the "Quick create new gauge from templates" modal for the user to select and be used to copy into a new gauge.
Tag/GaugeTemplateGroup/Caption: Gauge template group
Tag/GaugeTemplateGroup/Description: Grouping in template list
GaugeTemplate/SubscriptionTracker/Caption: Recurring Event Progress
GaugeTemplate/SubscriptionTracker/Description: Show recurring calendar entries as ECharts bars, with progress to the next due date.
GaugeTemplate/SubscriptionTracker/ChartTitle: Recurring Event Progress
GaugeTemplate/SubscriptionTracker/Empty: No recurring calendar entries to display
GaugeTemplate/SubscriptionTracker/Tooltip/NextDue: Next due
GaugeTemplate/SubscriptionTracker/Tooltip/NoNextDue: No upcoming occurrence
GaugeTemplate/SubscriptionTracker/Tooltip/RemainingDays: Days remaining
GaugeTemplate/SubscriptionTracker/Tooltip/Progress: Current cycle
Command/AddDualTagGraph/Caption: ➕ Create Dual Tag Relation Graph (Temp/Perm)
Command/AddDualTagGraph/Description: Create a dashboard item showing intersection of two tags
Command/AddDualTagGraph/startTiddler/Caption: Start Tag/Tiddler
Command/AddDualTagGraph/startTiddler/Description: Input the first tag or tiddler
Command/AddDualTagGraph/endTiddler/Caption: End Tag/Tiddler
Command/AddDualTagGraph/endTiddler/Description: Input the second tag or tiddler
Command/AddDualTagGraph/dashboardTitle/Caption: Dashboard Title (empty for temp)
Command/AddDualTagGraph/dashboardTitle/Description: Title for this dashboard (will be temp if left empty)
